"```sql\nSELECT \n    CAST(COUNT(DISTINCT df2.driverId) AS REAL) * 100 / COUNT(DISTINCT df1.driverId) AS percentage\nFROM \n    (SELECT results.driverId\n     FROM results\n     INNER JOIN races ON results.raceId = races.raceId\n     WHERE races.year BETWEEN 2000 AND 2005) AS df1\nINNER JOIN \n    (SELECT results.driverId\n     FROM results\n     INNER JOIN drivers ON results.driverId = drivers.driverId\n     WHERE YEAR(drivers.dob) < 1985 AND results.laps > 50) AS df2\nON df1.driverId = df2.driverId;\n```"